# Bake & Grill — Full Codebase Reference

Works alongside `admin-panel-audit.mdc` (admin panel bugs & missing pages), `deploy-commands.mdc` (server deploy), and `cms-architecture.mdc` (site settings CMS). Together they give full developer context.

