## Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Backend | Laravel 11, PHP 8.2, Sanctum, MySQL |
| Admin UI | React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Lucide icons, inline styles |
| Public site | Blade templates (extends `layout.blade.php`) |
| Shared types | `apps/shared/` — consumed by both admin and online-order apps |

```
