## Admin Dashboard (React)

**Entry:** `App.tsx` → `Routes` → 22 page components in `pages/`

**Auth flow:** `getMe()` on mount → stores `StaffUser` in state → `AuthGuard` / `RoleGuard` wraps protected routes

**API client:** `api.ts` uses `createApiClient` from `@shared/api` — reads token from `localStorage('admin_token')`, sets `Authorization: Bearer` header

**State:** React `useState` + `useEffect` only. No Redux/Zustand.

**Styling:** Inline JS objects everywhere. No CSS modules. Tailwind v4 is imported but avoided for component styles due to arbitrary-value rendering issues in v4.

**UI components:** `components/ui/` — Button, Card, Modal, Badge, Input, Tabs, Toast, Toggle, Spinner, EmptyState, Pagination. Shared layout primitives in `SharedUI.tsx`.

**Build output:** `apps/admin-dashboard/dist/` copied to `backend/public/admin/` before every commit.

