## Public Website (Blade)

`layout.blade.php` — shared header/footer, reads from `SiteSetting` (see `cms-architecture.mdc`)

Pages: `home.blade.php`, `contact.blade.php`, `privacy.blade.php`, `hours.blade.php`

All contact info, hero slides, categories, proof stats, CTA copy — fully DB-driven, editable from Admin → Settings → Website Settings.

